{"TopicId":154662,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Upvotes Not Working in Gameplay and Technical Support Subforums","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-07T22:11:23Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-07T22:11:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi Mods,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just ran a test on the upvoting system in the Gp\u0026amp;TS subforum. It appears that when you upvote a post and then reload the page, you can\u0027t un-upvote the post.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn a similar vein, upvoting and unupvoting a post leaves you unable to reupvote it until you reload the page. And once you reload the page from there, you can\u0027t unreupvote it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre these bugs or features? And if one (or both) are bugs, can you fix them, or is it up to IPS?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-07T22:11:53Z\u0022 title=\u002201/07/2017 10:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 7, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Dman979\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frybert","CreatedById":97766,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-07T22:24:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, seems to be no problem for me. \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/16426-sal_vager/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002216426\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/16426-sal_vager/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@sal_vager\u003C/a\u003E or another higher level admin might be able to help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-08T12:35:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTesting, will move this thread hold on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTested in all 3 of those forums, can\u0027t seem to reproduce it, but that might be due to my moderator permissions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-08T12:47:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just tested in the \u0022Fun with Trigonometry\u0022 thread. I was able to upvote (like) and unupvote (unlike) both the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E and a reply, both before and after reloading the page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-08T16:49:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-5thhorseman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002273725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-5thhorseman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@5thHorseman\u003C/a\u003E- I wasn\u0027t referring to the \u0022Like this\u0022 button, I meant the arrow. Is that what you did, too?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/16426-sal_vager/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002216426\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/16426-sal_vager/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@sal_vager\u003C/a\u003E- If it helps, I\u0027m on Firefox. If you know a free video software to record my screen, I can show you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-08T16:51:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\